getting-started.title: Getting Started
getting-started.description: Read this quick 1-minute guide to know how to navigate our StyleSheet system without any confusion.

overview.title: Overview
overview.description: Our music player UI is fully customizable using Roblox StyleSheets.

stylesheets/collect-page.title: Collect Page
stylesheets/collect-page.description: Styles elements found directly on the collect tab's page

stylesheets/customize-page.title: Customize Page
stylesheets/customize-page.description: Styles elements found anywhere on the customize tab's page

stylesheets/item-viewer-page.title: Item Viewer Page
stylesheets/item-viewer-page.description: Styles elements found directly on the interaction page of an individual item

stylesheets/library-page.title: Library Page
stylesheets/library-page.description: Styles elements found directly on the library tab's page

stylesheets/main-window.title: Main Window
stylesheets/main-window.description: Styles elements which are always visible, and are part of the overall core window

stylesheets/mixins.title: Mixins
stylesheets/mixins.description: Style elements which are re-used throughout the whole interface, which other StyleSheets can override

stylesheets/player.title: Player
stylesheets/player.description: Styles elements which are part of either the mini player or full player, for playing music

stylesheets/start-collect-page.title: Start Collect Page
stylesheets/start-collect-page.description: Styles elements which are on the next menu page, after pressing any button the collect tab's page

tokensheets/fonts.title: Fonts
tokensheets/fonts.description: Variables which change the appearance of text

tokensheets/icons.title: Icons
tokensheets/icons.description: Variables which change the icon assets used in the interface

tokensheets/palette.title: Palette
tokensheets/palette.description: Variables which change the color scheme of the whole interface

tokensheets/sizes.title: Sizes
tokensheets/sizes.description: Variables which change sizes of any elements, including icons and elements which change size dynamically

tokensheets/sounds.title: Sounds
tokensheets/sounds.description: Variables which change sound effects of user interactions

tokensheets/tweaks.title: Tweaks
tokensheets/tweaks.description: Variables which behaviour of the window, and some globally common visuals

tokensheets/window.title: Window
tokensheets/window.description: Variables which change core properties of the window
